---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Year of the Build">
  <article>
    <h1>About Year of the Build</h1>

    <section>
      <h2>The Challenge</h2>
      <p>
        Build and launch real projects. Continuously. Forever.
        Public accountability log documenting the entire journey.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What Counts as a Launch?</h2>
      <p>A project is considered "launched" when:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Public GitHub repository exists</li>
        <li>Landing page is live</li>
        <li>Posted in relevant subreddits</li>
        <li>Listed on Product Hunt (if applicable)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>The Goal</h2>
      <p>
        Ship consistently. Learn rapidly. Build a portfolio of real, launched products.
        No tutorial hell. No analysis paralysis. Just building and launching.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Follow Along</h2>
      <p>
        Subscribe to the newsletter to get weekly devlog updates delivered to your inbox.
        Each week includes progress updates, technical challenges, and lessons learned.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Alex Getty, founder of Getty Made LLC. This is my public commitment to
        build consistently and ship real products.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  article {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
